response.original_title: NJPW Presents CMLL Fantastica Mania 2019 - Jan 11, 2019 Osaka
response.overview: Fantastica Mania 2019 was a professional wrestling tour, scripted and co-produced by the Japanese New Japan Pro-Wrestling (NJPW) promotion and the Mexican Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre (CMLL) promotion. The tour started on January 11 and ran until January 21, 2019, with shows taking place in Osaka, Ehime, Kyoto, Gifu, Chiba and Tokyo.  At Osaka Prefectural Gym #2
response.title: NJPW Presents CMLL Fantastica Mania 2019 - Jan 11, 2019 Osaka
